---
title: Crispy Salmon and Green Beans with Green Onion Rice and Plum Sauce
description: This Thai-inspired dish is faster than takeout but hits all the right taste notes! You'll love the green onion rice paired with the crunch of crispy shallots. A sweet and savoury sauce brings it all together!
